==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
*From an obsolete φάω phaō (to shine or make manifest, especially by rays; compare G5316 and G5346); luminousness (in the widest application, natural or artificial, abstract or concrete, literal or figurative):

===Pronunciation===
*φῶς / phōs / foce

===Noun===
'''φῶς'''

# [[fire]], [[light]].

